{"tid":33770,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"自學python,求reference material","createTime":"2016-12-11T04:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T03:34:06.000Z","uid":40980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11548dc061d8f54b0d83ce7eb288cfe07e2bef5d","tid":33770,"uid":40980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"做會計，想發展多種能力，其實唔洗好專，只求做到基本野，不過對programming 0 認識<br />\n<br />\n而家上網睇緊Automate the Boring Stuff with Python, 其實仲有無多d參考書或者網頁？出去搵d 班讀下又抵唔抵？<br />\n<br />\n仲有初學電腦set up要點樣？我而家用緊mac book air,已裝 python 官網個3.5.2 installer。仲有無其他野要裝埋？我見上youtube有d教學prefer用iterm。其實係咪好d?但基本要點用？<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個好基本既問題，其實係mba有咩hotkey係split screen, window 我就識，但mac攪幾都唔得。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝咁多位連巴，腸油一定唔會少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2309e74af57fc42e2e94c7258d59081839a91c","tid":33770,"uid":6958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:59:36.000Z","msg":"自學緊programming， 留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb111f3a3bd9cb2784db61176377c69c53ee12b3","tid":33770,"uid":51145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:02:06.000Z","msg":"我教你 收你平d<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ccdc5d57cb4d1ccdd137a48116e18d5a585b53","tid":33770,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"Codecademy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05c43e738716e9a3d9f26e23beda55e97d7ce67","tid":33770,"uid":40980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Codecademy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\